## SimpleBlockNode.endToken property

The token for the closing token of the block. If the block is closed it will be the mirror variant of the `startToken`<!-- -->. If the block is unclosed, this will be an EOF token.

**Signature:**

```typescript
endToken: CSSToken;
```
